    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 116.</p><p>Obliterating Strike</p><p>Strike, Durandal</p><p>Weapon: Any heavy melee weapon Classes: Barbarian, Fighter, Paladin Channeling Time: 1 action Base LP Cost: 2 LP Range: Weapon range Duration: Instantaneous</p><p>You channel every ounce of your physical might into a single, annihilating blow. Make a melee weapon attack against a creature within reach. On a hit, the attack deals 5d10 x 10 Lethal damage. On a critical hit, you do not multiply the damage dice by 2, but instead deal 8d10 x 10 Lethal damage. A creature hit by this attack must succeed on a Constitution saving throw against your Mythical Technique save DC or be stunned for a minute and pushed up to 30 feet away from you.</p><p>One Use. Once you use this Mythical Technique, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
